"on_hold":0,"dropped":1,"wish":2,"collect":1,"doing":0},"id":577037,"eps":26,"meta_tags":["TV","原创","子供向","美国"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1985-09-09","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/a5/12/4735_Y55Fa.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/a5/12/4735_Y55Fa.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/a5/12/4735_Y55Fa.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/a5/12/4735_Y55Fa.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/a5/12/4735_Y55Fa.jpg"},"summary":"　　本片是《宇宙的巨人希曼》的“兄妹篇”，也是该片大获成功后的趁热打铁之作，由美国飞美逊公司（Filmation Associates）于1985年推出。希瑞的造型源自1941年问世的漫画《神奇女侠》（Wonder Woman）。\r\n　　每集中，少不了的开场白如下：“我叫阿多拉，霍曼的亲妹妹。我是水晶城堡的保护者。这，是顺马风，我的坐骑。有一天，我获得了奇迹般的秘密，当我抽出剑说：‘赐于我力量吧……She-Ra，She-Ra，She-Ra，She-Ra，我是希瑞……’我便和起义军的朋友们一起，为解救以希利亚，与罪恶的霍达克进行着战斗……”（关于阿多拉的身世之谜，霍达克正是她的养父！当年霍德人进攻艾特尼亚时，霍达克曾经从王宫里偷走一个女婴，该女婴就是阿多拉——她的孪生哥哥便是亚当王子，多年后，鹦鹉仙子令亚当救回了自己的妹妹，阿多拉这才知道了事实的真相。）","name":"She-Ra: Princess of Power","name_cn":"非凡的公主希瑞","tags":[{"name":"童年","count":32,"total_cont":0},{"name":"希瑞","count":31,"total_cont":0},{"name":"希曼","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"法国","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"没看完","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80年代","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80s","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补旧番","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Filmation_Associates","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1985","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"女神","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"没看全","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"非凡的公主希瑞"},{"key":"话数","value":"93"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"1985年9月9日"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"http://www.entertainmentrights.com/"},{"key":"播放电视台","value":"辛迪加"},{"key